27 provided directly (i) to the public or (ii) to such classes of users as
28 to be effectively available directly to the public.
29 Sec. 16. If any section in this act or any part of any section is
30 declared invalid or unconstitutional, the declaration shall not affect
31 the validity or constitutionality of the remaining portions.
